  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK388">
<l>muṟaiceytu kāppāṟṟum maṉṉavaṉ makkaṭ </l>
<l>kiṟaiyeṉṟu vaikkap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That king, will be esteemed a God among men, who performs his own duties, and protects (his subjects).</l>
            </lg>
